r716 | bertin | 2008-04-02 14:56:45 +0200 (Wed, 02 Apr 2008) | 2 lines

Merged --with-plplot and --without-plplot options in one single AC_ARG_WITH
(Greg Daues' suggestion).

------------------------------------------------------------------------
